Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:52.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれそうな夢の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:58.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}よろこびを探す世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:08.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はどんな輝きで　明日へと跳ぶの？　教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:14.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}声になった未来の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:20.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まりの my melody 聞こえた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:26.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY！ 空が青く高くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:31.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙ぐんだ今を忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:37.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひたすら進もうと誓うから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:41.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分かりあった瞬間は大切な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:44.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}ずっと一緒に　君と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:47.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていればいいね多分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:50.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒だ　君と一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:53.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在の鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:59.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY？ だから今を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:04.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誇らしくなるね君の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:10.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やたらに眩しいよその笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向かいあって本心は負けないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:52.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}灑落著夢的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:58.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是找尋著喜悅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:08.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你帶著怎樣的光芒 向著明日起航 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:20.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傾聽憧憬著未來的心跳 那是我邁向明天的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:26.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY! 無垠的天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:31.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘記今天的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好一起大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:41.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心靈相通的瞬間 是如此珍重的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:44.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}想要一直在一起 同你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:47.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有微笑就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:50.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在一起 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:53.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握通向明天的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:59.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY? 所以我相信現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:04.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的思念讓我自豪無比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:10.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑臉是那麼的光彩奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直面真心就不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:44.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}急に黙り込んで　君は手を繋いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}茜空に消えてく今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見送る長いかげぼうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:59.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}放課後は永遠みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}サヨナラをごまかしてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:13.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど心は旅立ちの予感を知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:20.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}果てしない未来への
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躊躇いを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:33.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑む君の夢が眩しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:39.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あと少しの季節を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惜しむようにはしゃいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:53.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日への帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:44.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}突然沉默不語的你 靜靜地把我的手握起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漸漸延向地平線的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}訴說著一天又隨著夕陽沉去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:59.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你說放學後的時光就像永恆一樣漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把離別的那一刻深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:13.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}但是彼此卻都深知即將各自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:25.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}掩飾著對未知旅途的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:33.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑著的你 夢想是那樣的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:39.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我們珍惜這所剩無幾的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盡情歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:53.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}然後踏上通往明天的歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  給我果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇呢  貴史君竟然會幫忙運送貨物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  很少見呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬語？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼一本正經啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同學什麼時候搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？  她說過要搬家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是下月底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴他紗季的郵箱地址了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  這種事得先徵求本人同意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表哥會不會去向紗季告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡過學長他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用過去式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明說過不喜歡比他小的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為紗季看上去很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要燙卷髮試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣撐不過一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕紗季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  如果我也變成紗季那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  紗季！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這突然是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼夏海會在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這裏是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是紗季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我是紗季嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是優香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成紗季了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你們幹的好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你是被撞傻了嗎  要不要去保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表哥  貴史君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海你以前也和他一起玩過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  紗季你有表哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海你去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去東京嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去  抱歉  下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能給你發郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  不就是約一次會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約… 你還有這種企圖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得變成紗季了  讓我也做一次白日夢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和學長一起出門的話優香不也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要裝成紗季的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  裝樣子也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海也有吧  只要在一起就會覺得滿足的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說Four Season的秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(407,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海成為了Four Season的一員  就當做是冬好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Fuyumi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個短暫的白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能變回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概實現我的願望就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會是絕對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香沒什麼體力才會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的身體好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨她進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了防止你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼許願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能夠恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠改變已經許下的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好許願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次  一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我更加真誠點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是變不回來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…被自己發火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想對自己發火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說的事不關己的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  優香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了要變回來  其它什麼事都不要去想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表情變得和紗季一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二  希望能恢復原樣  優香！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  夏海  這可是凜子的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你來幫點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺小凜好像有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  凜子非常有精神  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能暴露神石的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有去約會了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  凜子也只能回夏海家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海一直要為大樹準備午飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an8}（明天能見面嗎？）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會做點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼拌青菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼拌青菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水族館？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  聽說海豚奈緒子在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了中午看完企鵝之後去吃午飯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去看海獅表演  完了再去看海豚表演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就親親？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不親親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒什麼人的昏暗的水族館裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍一個人也沒有  於是在那裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就因為凜說了奇怪的話  我開始緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能裝得像紗季一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被發現是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也一直用這個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜不阻止我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我阻止你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香的願望就是我的願望  我支持你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  這是零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嗎  之前還總是求著要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…太好了太好了  我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香還真是一點都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成為Four Season一樣的偶像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼首先就要練習唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為偶像的話這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來郵件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早  給你們添麻煩了  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望馬上就能實現了  然後肯定能變回原樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  能再等一等的話我會很高興  優香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}（早上好）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  你打算睡到什麼時候  快起來  夏海  夏海！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}等等  這樣就像是在說我貪睡似的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找姐姐有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大樹  你出去玩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去叫你姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你朋友來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大樹  優香…不對  你知道紗季去哪裏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到她和男人走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的  坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到水族館要20分鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼拚命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不能跑的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點阻止優香的話  不知道她會做出什麼來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離演出還有點時間  進裏面去慢慢逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有暑假補習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒關係…不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  興奮過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是紗季  我是紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香也經常做那個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:16:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  比起那個你衣服沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺氣氛很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去  她要是想做什麼奇怪的事我們得馬上去阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的事是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…接吻什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎  第一次約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道  但是說不准吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴史就在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明也經常一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你了  我玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  如果就這樣一切都停止下來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴史君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  就直接叫我名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴史君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那你就叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也直接叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始我就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴史君喜歡的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在貴史君眼中的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香？  誰是優香？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打斷了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說過要支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想和他親親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已經沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎變回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥  我們要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了優香  我才有了這段美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了優香？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重  嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了  竟然連個表情符都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拒絕的郵件裏怎麼能加上心之類的表情符
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子都沒可能成為紗季的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然了  優香就是優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為  優香就是優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們來比誰先跑到便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰輸了請客喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  完全跑不動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香沒體力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦  你們等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  優香竟然用我的身體去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再追究了  都已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要追究  一定要報復她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要報復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是挨打不還手的紗季大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  你要忍住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇跡  第五話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱感冒和鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  就算是要報復  但你讓她得感冒真的是做得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  我還什麼都沒做啊
